    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering an uncompromising 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in collector-grade condition. This example features the S54B32 3.2L inline-six, exhibiting perfect compression across all cylinders and a valvetrain recently calibrated with precise shim adjustments. The mechanical symphony is managed by a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox with a short-throw action and a factory-spec M-Variable limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed: the rear subframe mounting points have been professionally reinforced, and the double-VANOS system has been overhauled with viton seals to ensure optimal variable valve timing. The suspension retains its original geometry with zero bushing deflection, providing the tactile feedback these chassis are renowned for. Finished in a flawless Carbon Black, the undercarriage is dry, and the interior Nappa leather remains supple with no bolster wear. A turnkey masterpiece for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 44500.0,
