      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly collector-grade example that redefines what it means to be 'pre-owned.' This vehicle has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment since day one, and the condition reflects that level of care. The exterior paint retains its deep, factory-fresh luster with zero swirl marks, scratches, or stone chips, further protected by a professionally applied ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom condition; the premium leather seats show no signs of bolster wear or creasing, and the interior still carries that distinct new-car aroma. Every button, switch, and electronic feature functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service history performed exclusively by certified technicians using OEM parts. It has never seen inclement weather and the undercarriage is as clean as the bodywork. The sale comes complete with all original keys, the factory window sticker, and a full set of owner\u2019s manuals. For the discerning buyer who refuses to settle for anything less than perfection, this is the one.",
